snippet.title: RocketPods - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
BUY NOW: 
https://firith.studio/rocketpods/

FIRITH STUDIO:
https://firith.studio

DISCORD: 
https://discordapp.com/invite/PfvQb42

Thrust your way through the galaxy's hardest obstacle courses! Learn how to control a RocketPod while also controlling your own frustration and fury. Start out as a novice, and leave as a Legend. Unlock the rarest RocketPods [collect 7 unique Pods], earn EXP, and attain new Rankings. Compare your pilot profile and mission results with your friends for competitive play! The galaxy of RocketPods is vast and replete with trillions of planets! Visit exotic gas giants that feature beautifully pre-rendered 3D artwork and animations!
